ISLAMABAD, Dec 30 (APP):Minister of State for Information and Broadcasting Farrukh Habib Thursday strongly condemned the blast in Quetta, claimed at least four lives and left over a dozen injured.
In a statement, he sympathized with the families of those who died in the tragic incident and prayed to Allah Almighty for early recovery of the injured.
